{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ff8321c8b0","title":"关于和国民党谈判条件等事致潘汉年电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"645b00740c","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":10,"articleId":"ff8321c8b0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f3fc7fb4db","type":"paragraph","text":"关于和国民党谈判条件等事","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0"},{"id":"d2b48d2286","type":"paragraph","text":"致潘汉年电","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0"},{"id":"c001d7955a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月10日）汉年同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0"},{"id":"751ff3f63e","type":"paragraph","text":"齐电悉。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0"},{"id":"45da35c8bb","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、合作为实行抗日救亡，但至今天蒋介石似尚无抗日救亡之决心，合作谈判缺乏必要之前提，南京抗日派诸君如不能促成蒋氏此种决心，则谈判显无速成之望","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0"},{"id":"c8309856a5","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、根本不能同意蒋氏对外妥协对内昔求之政策，更根本拒绝其悔唇红军之态度。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0"},{"id":"34fee0ae0d","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、红军在彼方忠实的与明确的承认其参加抗日救亡之前提下，可以改换抗日番号，划定抗日防地，服从抗日指挥。在这些上面我们并不坚持形式上的平等，也不须用两个政府出面谈判，但是必须两党（不是两政府）平等的签订抗日救亡之政治军事协定，红军不能减少一兵一卒，而且须要扩充之，离开实行抗日救亡任务，无任何商量余地。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0"},{"id":"03857b264a","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、彼方如有诚意，须立即停止进攻并将军队撤退于苏区以外，静【候】谈判之结果。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0"},{"id":"889e4094f1","type":"paragraph","text":"杨子任蒸西","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0"}],"page":{"id":"04781496eb","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ff8321c8b0","start":152,"end":152}}}},"__N_SSG":true}